                </p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-i18n="hero.cta">Start Free Trial</a>
                    <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" data-i18n="hero.learn">Learn More</a>
